trans-unit.source: Why do I get this message when I try to queue my build?
trans-unit.target: Why do I get this message when I try to queue my build?

trans-unit.source: When you try to queue a build, you might get a message such as: "No agent could be found with the following capabilities: msbuild, vsiualstudio, vstest."
trans-unit.target: When you try to queue a build, you might get a message such as: "No agent could be found with the following capabilities: msbuild, vsiualstudio, vstest."

trans-unit.source: One common cause of this problem is that you need to install prerequisite software such as Visual Studio on the machine where the build agent is running.
trans-unit.target: One common cause of this problem is that you need to install prerequisite software such as Visual Studio on the machine where the build agent is running.
